		<articleText><![CDATA[<p class="leading3">We truly appreciate your interest in this association, however to be part of it there are a few applications to be filled out.
1. Please fill out the  <a href="http://www.houstonredcross.org/attachments/wysiwyg/28/YouthVolunteerApplicationForm.pdf">YOUTH VOLUNTEER APPLICATION FORM</a>.
2. View the  <a href="http://www.redcross.org/flash/course01_v01/">AMERICAN RED CROSS ONLINE DISASTER TRAINING</a>.
3. Then fill out the Online Disaster Training course, please completely fill out this  <a href="http://westernct.redcross.org/documents/5898H.pdf">APPLICATION FOR DISASTER TRAINING SYSTEM</a>.
4. As part of the membership completion, you will need to attend an official Red Cross orientation. (More information will added for this later.)
6. There will be a fee for this club. Fees have not been decided yet, but it will be around $15.00.
7. We will be having a t-shirt as well. Designs will be added as the next school year approaches.
All of these items must be enclosed in an envelope with your name, grade level, and a checklist of all of your items on the front. If you do not have everything within this envelope, it will be considered invalid. (This will be edited with more accurate information, for now this should provide abdurate  the process. This application was adapted from that of Hightower’s Red Cross Association)

